reviewText:
Possibly one of the better mecha series ever made.
I have the old Geneon box, but for a full series and a movie, this is great deal and I would strongly consider getting it.

Saw this back on Funimation Channel around 2013 I think.  Basically it's about a group of people, children piloting things called Fafners battling  aliens called Festum and they're on an island.  Is all I can say since I can't really deal much of a review.  Also the A.I. (Anime Industry) just made a sequel called Exodus for this series as I heard.

Poor animation quality. Story seems to be complete and would possibly rate it higher if I was able to stay interested long enough to finish the series but haven't been able to finish it. Fortunately thanks to the SAVE edition I didn't waste a lot of money on this.

Great series! Once again S.A.V.E gave a great price for a great series. The scenes and art were rendered quite well and the dubbing was done very well. I would recommend this series be added to anyone's coll
good series, nice Mechas as well plot line
I love this series and Met my expectations and delivery was in a timely manner.
